To find the $\goldE{\text{total}}$ number of spells Anna's wand can cast, we start with the number of spells $\blueE{\text{Elsa's wand}}$ can cast, and add the number of $\maroonD{\text{fewer spells}}$ Elsa's wand casts.

![](web+graphie:${☣ LOCALPATH}/images/88b003b33bed6caa8907b084de7eafcb0e1a69b3)

$\begin{align}
\blueE{\text{Elsa's wand}} + \maroonD{17}  &= \goldE{\text{Anna's spells}} \\\\
\blueE{53} + \maroonD{17} &= \goldE{\Box}
\end{align}$

To find the $\goldE{\text{total}}$ height of the Dragon's house, we start with the height of the $\blueE{\text{Giant's house}}$, and add how many $\maroonD{\text{meters shorter}}$ it is.

![](web+graphie:${☣ LOCALPATH}/images/74c29a58dbaab6798cdc3e5aebcc0a9518aca123)

$\begin{align}
\blueE{\text{Giant's house}} + \maroonD{35}  &= \goldE{\text{Dragon's house}} \\\\
\blueE{23} + \maroonD{35} &= \goldE{\Box}
\end{align}$

To find the $\goldE{\text{total}}$ number of capitals Ari can name, we start with the number of capitals $\blueE{\text{Rani}}$ can name, and add how many $\maroonD{\text{fewer}}$ names she can name than Ari.

![](web+graphie:${☣ LOCALPATH}/images/b7c4efcbdc13153ed30ec9233639c8cb41f02836)

$\begin{align}
\blueE{\text{Rani}} + \maroonD{21}  &= \goldE{\text{Ari}} \\\\
\blueE{48} + \maroonD{21} &= \goldE{\Box}
\end{align}$

To find the $\goldE{\text{total}}$ height to the window, we start with the $\blueE{\text{length of the rope}}$, and add how many $\maroonD{\text{meters shorter}}$ the rope is. 

![](web+graphie:${☣ LOCALPATH}/images/4a007e41290775aaaed5c76e2bef9ea45bd86a78)

$\begin{align}
\blueE{\text{Length of the rope}} + \maroonD{12}  &= \goldE{\text{Height of the window}} \\\\
\blueE{19} + \maroonD{12} &= \goldE{\Box}
\end{align}$

